    <section ids="swift-backup-driver" names="swift\ backup\ driver">
        <title>Swift backup driver</title>
        <paragraph>The backup driver for the swift back end performs a volume backup to an
            object storage system.</paragraph>
        <paragraph>To enable the swift backup driver, include the following option in the
            <literal>cinder.conf</literal> file:</paragraph>
        <literal_block highlight_args="{}" language="ini" linenos="False" xml:space="preserve">backup_driver = cinder.backup.drivers.swift</literal_block>
        <paragraph>The following configuration options are available for the Swift back-end
            backup driver.</paragraph>
